<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<worksheet>
  <title>GR-2 Polynomial Functions</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>
      <alert>Instructions:</alert> Once you open the quiz, your timer begins.  I would recommend having an additional timer
        that goes off about 5 minutes prior, so that you know when to start uploading your work.
    </p>
    <p> Write out complete solutions to the following problems.</p>
  </introduction>

  <page>
    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>
          Given the function <m>f(x)=-2(x-1)^3(x+2)(x-3)</m>.
          <ol>
            <li>State the degree and leading coefficient of <m>f(x)</m>.</li>
            <li>State the end behavior of <m>f(x)</m>, using correct notation.</li>
            <li>State the x-intercepts and y-intercept of <m>f(x)</m>.</li>
          </ol>
        </p>
      </statement>
    </exercise>
    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>Given the function <m>p(x)=x^4+2x^3-3x^2-4x+4</m>.
          <ol>
            <li>State the end behavior of <m>p(x)</m>, using correct notation.</li>
            <li>Write <m>p(x)</m> in factored form.</li>
            <li>Sketch the graph of <m>p(x)</m>, showing the correct intercepts 
              and general behavior.</li>
          </ol>
        </p>
      </statement>
    </exercise>
  </page>
</worksheet>
